    <p>Make a new new remote upstream with git remote add upstream https://github.com/ajcanlas-tip/sysad2-12021.git</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Create a playbook that install java via package manager , and install boto,ansible,and openstack py packages using pip in both Ubuntu and Centos.</p>
